# Hjerterum / Boly Design System

**Canonical docs:** `docs/hjerterum/DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`, `docs/hjerterum/PRD.md` §15

## Universal Boly Standard (B-O-L-Y)

Every page — app, **Finn**, **Los**, Ops, landing — same professional Boly look. Dark default. No white-screen modules.

## Theme (locked)

- **Default: dark** on all features including Finn and Los
- **Toggle:** user chooses dark or light on every page
- **Logged in:** preference persists across sessions (`profiles.preferred_theme` + localStorage per user)
- **Guest:** localStorage on device
- Retire always-light `finn.css` / `los.css`

## Languages (locked)

**Only three locales:** `no` (Norwegian), `se` (Sámi), `en` (English).

- **Sámi on everything** — every string needs a `se` key; ship gate
- **`se` = Sámi** — not Swedish
- Swedish and Danish: **out of scope** — do not add

## Implementation

- `globals.css` + `[data-theme]`
- Design-system components; no `alert()`/`confirm()`
- i18n: `lib/i18n/*` with `no`, `se`, `en` for every key
